{
  "video_id": "OzA6jRYjVQs",
  "title": "A global food crisis may be less than a decade away | Sara Menker",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12580.0,
      "end_time": 16476.0,
      "text": "Since 2009, the world has been stuck"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16500.0,
      "end_time": 21636.0,
      "text": "on a single narrative around a coming global food crisis"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21660.0,
      "end_time": 24100.0,
      "text": "and what we need to do to avoid it."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24860.0,
      "end_time": 29220.0,
      "text": "How do we feed nine billion people by 2050?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 34876.0,
      "text": "Every conference, podcast and dialogue around global food security"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 34900.0,
      "end_time": 36596.0,
      "text": "starts with this question"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36620.0,
      "end_time": 38355.0,
      "text": "and goes on to answer it"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38380.0,
      "end_time": 42820.0,
      "text": "by saying we need to produce 70 percent more food."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 44980.0,
      "end_time": 47796.0,
      "text": "The 2050 narrative started to evolve"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 47820.0,
      "end_time": 52700.0,
      "text": "shortly after global food prices hit all-time highs in 2008."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 56360.0,
      "text": "People were suffering and struggling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 56600.0,
      "end_time": 57596.0,
      "text": "governments and world leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 57620.0,
      "end_time": 60236.0,
      "text": "needed to show us that they were paying attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 60260.0,
      "end_time": 61860.0,
      "text": "and were working to solve it."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63580.0,
      "end_time": 67356.0,
      "text": "The thing is, 2050 is so far into the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67380.0,
      "end_time": 69380.0,
      "text": "that we can&#39;t even relate to it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 70100.0,
      "end_time": 71836.0,
      "text": "and more importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 71860.0,
      "end_time": 74116.0,
      "text": "if we keep doing what we&#39;re doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 74140.0,
      "end_time": 76500.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s going to hit us a lot sooner than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77900.0,
      "end_time": 81180.0,
      "text": "I believe we need to ask a different question."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 82100.0,
      "end_time": 84436.0,
      "text": "The answer to that question"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 84460.0,
      "end_time": 87200.0,
      "text": "needs to be framed differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 88940.0,
      "end_time": 91676.0,
      "text": "If we can reframe the old narrative"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 91700.0,
      "end_time": 94156.0,
      "text": "and replace it with new numbers"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 94180.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "that tell us a more complete pictures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 97540.0,
      "end_time": 100716.0,
      "text": "numbers that everyone can understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100740.0,
      "end_time": 101940.0,
      "text": "and relate to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 103140.0,
      "end_time": 105820.0,
      "text": "we can avoid the crisis altogether."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 108380.0,
      "end_time": 111235.0,
      "text": "I was a commodities trader in my past life"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 113436.0,
      "text": "and one of the things that I learned trading"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 113460.0,
      "end_time": 116339.0,
      "text": "is that every market has a tipping point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 117180.0,
      "end_time": 120756.0,
      "text": "the point at which change occurs so rapidly"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 120780.0,
      "end_time": 122636.0,
      "text": "that it impacts the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122660.0,
      "end_time": 124619.0,
      "text": "and things change forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 125900.0,
      "end_time": 128500.0,
      "text": "Think of the last financial crisis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 129620.0,
      "end_time": 131300.0,
      "text": "or the dot-com crash."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 132740.0,
      "end_time": 135600.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s my concern."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 136580.0,
      "end_time": 138636.0,
      "text": "We could have a tipping point"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 138660.0,
      "end_time": 140796.0,
      "text": "in global food and agriculture"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140820.0,
      "end_time": 142715.0,
      "text": "if surging demand"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 142739.0,
      "end_time": 149140.0,
      "text": "surpasses the agricultural system&#39;s structural capacity to produce food."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 150600.0,
      "end_time": 154796.0,
      "text": "This means at this point supply can no longer keep up with demand"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 154820.0,
      "end_time": 157760.0,
      "text": "despite exploding prices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 157100.0,
      "end_time": 161180.0,
      "text": "unless we can commit to some type of structural change."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 162380.0,
      "end_time": 164156.0,
      "text": "This time around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 164180.0,
      "end_time": 166756.0,
      "text": "it won&#39;t be about stock markets and money."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 166780.0,
      "end_time": 168156.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about people."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 168180.0,
      "end_time": 171580.0,
      "text": "People could starve and governments may fall."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 173200.0,
      "end_time": 177556.0,
      "text": "This question of at what point does supply struggle"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 177580.0,
      "end_time": 179236.0,
      "text": "to keep up with surging demand"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 182916.0,
      "text": "is one that started off as an interest for me while I was trading"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 182940.0,
      "end_time": 185716.0,
      "text": "and became an absolute obsession."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 185740.0,
      "end_time": 188676.0,
      "text": "It went from interest to obsession"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 188700.0,
      "end_time": 192356.0,
      "text": "when I realized through my research how broken the system was"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 192380.0,
      "end_time": 196700.0,
      "text": "and how very little data was being used to make such critical decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 197460.0,
      "end_time": 201716.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the point I decided to walk away from a career on Wall Street"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 201740.0,
      "end_time": 204236.0,
      "text": "and start an entrepreneurial journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 206220.0,
      "text": "to start Gro Intelligence."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 206700.0,
      "end_time": 210196.0,
      "text": "At Gro, we focus on bringing this data"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 210220.0,
      "end_time": 212476.0,
      "text": "and doing the work to make it actionable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 212500.0,
      "end_time": 215500.0,
      "text": "to empower decision-makers at every level."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 216700.0,
      "end_time": 218316.0,
      "text": "But doing this work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 218340.0,
      "end_time": 220596.0,
      "text": "we also realized that the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 220620.0,
      "end_time": 222276.0,
      "text": "not just world leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 222300.0,
      "end_time": 226556.0,
      "text": "but businesses and citizens like every single person in this room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 226580.0,
      "end_time": 228660.0,
      "text": "lacked an actionable guide"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 229580.0,
      "end_time": 234196.0,
      "text": "on how we can avoid a coming global food security crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 234220.0,
      "end_time": 236236.0,
      "text": "And so we built a model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239155.0,
      "text": "leveraging the petabytes of data we sit on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 239180.0,
      "end_time": 241580.0,
      "text": "and we solved for the tipping point."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 242380.0,
      "end_time": 245996.0,
      "text": "Now, no one knows we&#39;ve been working on this problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 246200.0,
      "end_time": 249620.0,
      "text": "and this is the first time that I&#39;m sharing what we discovered."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 252200.0,
      "end_time": 256660.0,
      "text": "We discovered that the tipping point is actually a decade from now."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 258100.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260436.00000000003,
      "text": "We discovered that the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 260459.0,
      "end_time": 264820.0,
      "text": "will be short 214 trillion calories"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 266780.0,
      "end_time": 268219.0,
      "text": "by 2027."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 273600.0,
      "text": "The world is not in a position to fill this gap."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 274220.0,
      "end_time": 275820.0,
      "text": "Now, you&#39;ll notice"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 276780.0,
      "end_time": 281750.0,
      "text": "that the way I&#39;m framing this is different from how I started,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 281100.0,
      "end_time": 283236.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s intentional, because until now"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 286476.0,
      "text": "this problem has been quantified using mass:"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 286500.0,
      "end_time": 289316.0,
      "text": "think kilograms, tons, hectograms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 289340.0,
      "end_time": 291419.0,
      "text": "whatever your unit of choice is in mass."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 292100.0,
      "end_time": 294700.0,
      "text": "Why do we talk about food in terms of weight?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 295180.0,
      "end_time": 296596.0,
      "text": "Because it&#39;s easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 296620.0,
      "end_time": 300116.0,
      "text": "We can look at a photograph and determine tonnage on a ship"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 300140.0,
      "end_time": 302395.0,
      "text": "by using a simple pocket calculator."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 302420.0,
      "end_time": 305180.0,
      "text": "We can weigh trucks, airplanes and oxcarts."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 305700.0,
      "end_time": 309740.0,
      "text": "But what we care about in food is nutritional value."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 310860.0,
      "end_time": 313996.0,
      "text": "Not all foods are created equal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 314200.0,
      "end_time": 315780.0,
      "text": "even if they weigh the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 316740.0,
      "end_time": 319196.0,
      "text": "This I learned firsthand"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 319220.0,
      "end_time": 322220.0,
      "text": "when I moved from Ethiopia to the US for university."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 323200.0,
      "end_time": 325156.0,
      "text": "Upon my return back home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 325180.0,
      "end_time": 328396.0,
      "text": "my father, who was so excited to see me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 328420.0,
      "end_time": 332200.0,
      "text": "greeted me by asking why I was fat."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 332780.0,
      "end_time": 338556.0,
      "text": "Now, turns out that eating"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 338580.0,
      "end_time": 343436.0,
      "text": "approximately the same amount of food as I did in Ethiopia, but in America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 343460.0,
      "end_time": 346700.0,
      "text": "had actually lent a certain fullness to my figure."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 348580.0,
      "end_time": 352676.0,
      "text": "This is why we should care about calories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 352700.0,
      "end_time": 354356.0,
      "text": "not about mass."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 354380.0,
      "end_time": 357140.0,
      "text": "It is calories which sustain us."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 358700.0,
      "end_time": 364515.0,
      "text": "So 214 trillion calories is a very large number,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 364540.0,
      "end_time": 367676.0,
      "text": "and not even the most dedicated of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 367700.0,
      "end_time": 370635.0,
      "text": "think in the hundreds of trillions of calories."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 370660.0,
      "end_time": 372780.0,
      "text": "So let me break this down differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 373700.0,
      "end_time": 377360.0,
      "text": "An alternative way to think about this"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 377600.0,
      "end_time": 379916.0,
      "text": "is to think about it in Big Macs."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 379940.0,
      "end_time": 382556.0,
      "text": "214 trillion calories."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 382580.0,
      "end_time": 385796.0,
      "text": "A single Big Mac has 563 calories."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 385820.0,
      "end_time": 392360.0,
      "text": "That means the world will be short 379 billion Big Macs in 2027."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 392600.0,
      "end_time": 396600.0,
      "text": "That is more Big Macs than McDonald&#39;s has ever produced."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 397780.0,
      "end_time": 401835.0,
      "text": "So how did we get to these numbers in the first place?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 401860.0,
      "end_time": 403600.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re not made up."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 404220.0,
      "end_time": 409360.0,
      "text": "This map shows you where the world was 40 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 409600.0,
      "end_time": 413760.0,
      "text": "It shows you net calorie gaps in every country in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 413100.0,
      "end_time": 414556.0,
      "text": "Now, simply put,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 414580.0,
      "end_time": 417596.0,
      "text": "this is just calories consumed in that country"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 417620.0,
      "end_time": 420676.0,
      "text": "minus calories produced in that same country."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 420700.0,
      "end_time": 423476.0,
      "text": "This is not a statement on malnutrition or anything else."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 423500.0,
      "end_time": 427516.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s simply saying how many calories are consumed in a single year"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 427540.0,
      "end_time": 429396.0,
      "text": "minus how many are produced."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 429420.0,
      "end_time": 432796.0,
      "text": "Blue countries are net calorie exporters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 432820.0,
      "end_time": 434195.0,
      "text": "or self-sufficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 434220.0,
      "end_time": 436260.0,
      "text": "They have some in storage for a rainy day."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 436900.0,
      "end_time": 439715.0,
      "text": "Red countries are net calorie importers."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 439740.0,
      "end_time": 441676.0,
      "text": "The deeper, the brighter the red,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 441700.0,
      "end_time": 442940.0,
      "text": "the more you&#39;re importing."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 444200.0,
      "end_time": 448476.0,
      "text": "40 years ago, such few countries were net exporters of calories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 448500.0,
      "end_time": 450720.0,
      "text": "I could count them with one hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 451180.0,
      "end_time": 453276.0,
      "text": "Most of the African continent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 453300.0,
      "end_time": 455916.0,
      "text": "Europe, most of Asia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 455940.0,
      "end_time": 457956.0,
      "text": "South America excluding Argentina,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 457980.0,
      "end_time": 459700.0,
      "text": "were all net importers of calories."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 460380.0,
      "end_time": 464000.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s surprising is that China used to actually be food self-sufficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 464500.0,
      "end_time": 467460.0,
      "text": "India was a big net importer of calories."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 468900.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "40 years later, this is today."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 471780.0,
      "end_time": 475260.0,
      "text": "You can see the drastic transformation that&#39;s occurred in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 475860.0,
      "end_time": 479356.0,
      "text": "Brazil has emerged as an agricultural powerhouse."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 479380.0,
      "end_time": 482635.0,
      "text": "Europe is dominant in global agriculture."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 482660.0,
      "end_time": 485636.0,
      "text": "India has actually flipped from red to blue."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 485660.0,
      "end_time": 487916.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s become food self-sufficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 487940.0,
      "end_time": 490396.0,
      "text": "And China went from that light blue"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 490420.0,
      "end_time": 493600.0,
      "text": "to the brightest red that you see on this map."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 494100.0,
      "end_time": 496460.0,
      "text": "How did we get here? What happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 497780.0,
      "end_time": 500619.0,
      "text": "So this chart shows you India and Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 501260.0,
      "end_time": 503580.0,
      "text": "Blue line is India, red line is Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 504260.0,
      "end_time": 508396.0,
      "text": "How is it that two regions that started off so similarly"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 508420.0,
      "end_time": 510556.0,
      "text": "in such similar trajectories"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 510580.0,
      "end_time": 512716.0,
      "text": "take such different paths?"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 512740.0,
      "end_time": 514780.0,
      "text": "India had a green revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 515820.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519916.00000000006,
      "text": "Not a single African country had a green revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 519940.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521156.00000000006,
      "text": "The net outcome?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 521179.0,
      "end_time": 522876.0,
      "text": "India is food self-sufficient"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 522900.0,
      "end_time": 526276.0,
      "text": "and in the past decade has actually been exporting calories."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 526300.0,
      "end_time": 530260.0,
      "text": "The African continent now imports over 300 trillion calories a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 531100.0,
      "end_time": 535396.0,
      "text": "Then we add China, the green line."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 535420.0,
      "end_time": 538990.0,
      "text": "Remember the switch from the blue to the bright red?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 538940.0,
      "end_time": 541996.0,
      "text": "What happened and when did it happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 542200.0,
      "end_time": 544876.0,
      "text": "China seemed to be on a very similar path to India"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 544900.0,
      "end_time": 547675.0,
      "text": "until the start of the 21st century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 547700.0,
      "end_time": 549380.0,
      "text": "where it suddenly flipped."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 550220.0,
      "end_time": 552236.0,
      "text": "A young and growing population"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 552260.0,
      "end_time": 555356.0,
      "text": "combined with significant economic growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 555380.0,
      "end_time": 557796.0,
      "text": "made its mark with a big bang"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 557820.0,
      "end_time": 560300.0,
      "text": "and no one in the markets saw it coming."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 561340.0,
      "end_time": 565760.0,
      "text": "This flip was everything to global agricultural markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 565100.0,
      "end_time": 567916.0,
      "text": "Luckily now, South America"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 567940.0,
      "end_time": 573156.0,
      "text": "was starting to boom at the same time as China&#39;s rise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 573180.0,
      "end_time": 577180.0,
      "text": "and so therefore, supply and demand were still somewhat balanced."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 578140.0,
      "end_time": 579540.0,
      "text": "So the question becomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 580460.0,
      "end_time": 582600.0,
      "text": "where do we go from here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 583620.0,
      "end_time": 585156.0,
      "text": "Oddly enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 585180.0,
      "end_time": 586380.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not a new story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 587620.0,
      "end_time": 590996.0,
      "text": "except this time it&#39;s not just a story of China."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 591200.0,
      "end_time": 593396.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a continuation of China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 593420.0,
      "end_time": 595516.0,
      "text": "an amplification of Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 595540.0,
      "end_time": 597500.0,
      "text": "and a paradigm shift in India."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 598420.0,
      "end_time": 599939.0,
      "text": "By 2023,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 600820.0,
      "end_time": 605876.0,
      "text": "Africa&#39;s population is forecasted to overtake that of India&#39;s and China&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 605900.0,
      "end_time": 608555.0,
      "text": "By 2023, these three regions combined"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 608580.0,
      "end_time": 611740.0,
      "text": "will make up over half the world&#39;s population."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 613220.0,
      "end_time": 617236.0,
      "text": "This crossover point starts to present really interesting challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 617260.0,
      "end_time": 618996.0,
      "text": "for global food security."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 619200.0,
      "end_time": 622420.0,
      "text": "And a few years later, we&#39;re hit hard with that reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 623940.0,
      "end_time": 627300.0,
      "text": "What does the world look like in 10 years?"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 628940.0,
      "end_time": 632836.0,
      "text": "So far, as I mentioned, India has been food self-sufficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 632860.0,
      "end_time": 636260.0,
      "text": "Most forecasters predict that this will continue."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 637200.0,
      "end_time": 638220.0,
      "text": "We disagree."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 638980.0,
      "end_time": 643116.0,
      "text": "India will soon become a net importer of calories."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 643140.0,
      "end_time": 645396.0,
      "text": "This will be driven both by the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 645420.0,
      "end_time": 648915.0,
      "text": "that demand is growing from a population growth standpoint"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 648940.0,
      "end_time": 650196.0,
      "text": "plus economic growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 650220.0,
      "end_time": 651476.0,
      "text": "It will be driven by both."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 651500.0,
      "end_time": 654196.0,
      "text": "And even if you have optimistic assumptions"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 654220.0,
      "end_time": 656116.0,
      "text": "around production growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 656140.0,
      "end_time": 658260.0,
      "text": "it will make that slight flip."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 658780.0,
      "end_time": 662699.0,
      "text": "That slight flip can have huge implications."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 663620.0,
      "end_time": 668156.0,
      "text": "Next, Africa will continue to be a net importer of calories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 668180.0,
      "end_time": 671180.0,
      "text": "again driven by population growth and economic growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 671940.0,
      "end_time": 675836.0,
      "text": "This is again assuming optimistic production growth assumptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 675860.0,
      "end_time": 677276.0,
      "text": "Then China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 677300.0,
      "end_time": 679876.0,
      "text": "where population is flattening out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 679900.0,
      "end_time": 681876.0,
      "text": "calorie consumption will explode"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 681900.0,
      "end_time": 684915.0,
      "text": "because the types of calories consumed"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 684940.0,
      "end_time": 688460.0,
      "text": "are also starting to be higher-calorie-content foods."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 689420.0,
      "end_time": 691156.0,
      "text": "And so therefore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 691180.0,
      "end_time": 693360.0,
      "text": "these three regions combined"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 693600.0,
      "end_time": 696356.0,
      "text": "start to present a really interesting challenge for the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 696380.0,
      "end_time": 700476.0,
      "text": "Until now, countries with calorie deficits"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 700500.0,
      "end_time": 703760.0,
      "text": "have been able to meet these deficits"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 703100.0,
      "end_time": 704940.0,
      "text": "by importing from surplus regions."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 705540.0,
      "end_time": 708356.0,
      "text": "By surplus regions, I&#39;m talking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 708380.0,
      "end_time": 711516.0,
      "text": "North America, South America and Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 711540.0,
      "end_time": 713956.0,
      "text": "This line chart over here shows you"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 713980.0,
      "end_time": 718276.0,
      "text": "the growth and the projected growth over the next decade of production"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 718300.0,
      "end_time": 720596.0,
      "text": "from North America, South America and Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 720620.0,
      "end_time": 722360.0,
      "text": "What it doesn&#39;t show you"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 722600.0,
      "end_time": 725500.0,
      "text": "is that most of this growth is actually going to come from South America."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 726460.0,
      "end_time": 727876.0,
      "text": "And most of this growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 727900.0,
      "end_time": 732300.0,
      "text": "is going to come at the huge cost of deforestation."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 734600.0,
      "end_time": 737835.0,
      "text": "And so when you look at the combined demand increase"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 737860.0,
      "end_time": 741180.0,
      "text": "coming from India, China and the African continent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 742200.0,
      "end_time": 744836.0,
      "text": "and look at it versus the combined increase in production"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 744860.0,
      "end_time": 747636.0,
      "text": "coming from India, China, the African continent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 747660.0,
      "end_time": 750200.0,
      "text": "North America, South America and Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 751100.0,
      "end_time": 756516.0,
      "text": "you are left with a 214-trillion-calorie deficit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 756540.0,
      "end_time": 758276.0,
      "text": "one we can&#39;t produce."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 758300.0,
      "end_time": 762236.0,
      "text": "And this, by the way, is actually assuming we take all the extra calories"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 762260.0,
      "end_time": 764641.0,
      "text": "produced in North America, South America and Europe"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 765700.0,
      "end_time": 769940.0,
      "text": "and export them solely to India, China and Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 771200.0,
      "end_time": 774500.0,
      "text": "What I just presented to you is a vision of an impossible world."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 775340.0,
      "end_time": 777180.0,
      "text": "We can do something to change that."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 778220.0,
      "end_time": 780516.0,
      "text": "We can change consumption patterns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 780540.0,
      "end_time": 782795.0,
      "text": "we can reduce food waste,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 782820.0,
      "end_time": 786360.0,
      "text": "or we can make a bold commitment"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 786600.0,
      "end_time": 788380.0,
      "text": "to increasing yields exponentially."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 789540.0,
      "end_time": 791675.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m not going to go into discussing"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 791700.0,
      "end_time": 794196.0,
      "text": "changing consumption patterns or reducing food waste,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 794220.0,
      "end_time": 797276.0,
      "text": "because those conversations have been going on for some time now."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 797300.0,
      "end_time": 798516.0,
      "text": "Nothing has happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 798540.0,
      "end_time": 801996.0,
      "text": "Nothing has happened because those arguments"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 802200.0,
      "end_time": 804956.0,
      "text": "ask the surplus regions to change their behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 804980.0,
      "end_time": 807420.0,
      "text": "on behalf of deficit regions."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 808700.0,
      "end_time": 811276.0,
      "text": "Waiting for others to change their behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 811300.0,
      "end_time": 813795.0,
      "text": "on your behalf, for your survival,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 813820.0,
      "end_time": 815316.0,
      "text": "is a terrible idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 815340.0,
      "end_time": 816940.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s unproductive."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 817380.0,
      "end_time": 822100.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;d like to suggest an alternative that comes from the red regions."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 823780.0,
      "end_time": 826156.0,
      "text": "China, India, Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 826180.0,
      "end_time": 829476.0,
      "text": "China is constrained in terms of how much more land it actually has"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 829500.0,
      "end_time": 831360.0,
      "text": "available for agriculture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 831600.0,
      "end_time": 834835.0,
      "text": "and it has massive water resource availability issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 834860.0,
      "end_time": 838500.0,
      "text": "So the answer really lies in India and in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 839660.0,
      "end_time": 844596.0,
      "text": "India has some upside in terms of potential yield increases."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 844620.0,
      "end_time": 847196.0,
      "text": "Now this is the gap between its current yield"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 847220.0,
      "end_time": 850340.0,
      "text": "and the theoretical maximum yield it can achieve."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 851540.0,
      "end_time": 854756.0,
      "text": "It has some unfarmed arable land remaining, but not much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 854780.0,
      "end_time": 857600.0,
      "text": "India is quite land-constrained."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 858600.0,
      "end_time": 860715.0,
      "text": "Now, the African continent, on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 860740.0,
      "end_time": 864360.0,
      "text": "has vast amounts of arable land remaining"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 864600.0,
      "end_time": 866739.0,
      "text": "and significant upside potential in yields."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 867900.0,
      "end_time": 869996.0,
      "text": "Somewhat simplified picture here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 870200.0,
      "end_time": 875360.0,
      "text": "but if you look at sub-Saharan African yields in corn today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 875600.0,
      "end_time": 878540.0,
      "text": "they are where North American yields were in 1940."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 880420.0,
      "end_time": 884156.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have 70-plus years to figure this out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 884180.0,
      "end_time": 886715.0,
      "text": "so it means we need to try something new"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 886740.0,
      "end_time": 888900.0,
      "text": "and we need to try something different."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 890220.0,
      "end_time": 892380.0,
      "text": "The solution starts with reforms."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 893700.0,
      "end_time": 897676.0,
      "text": "We need to reform and commercialize"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 897700.0,
      "end_time": 900236.0,
      "text": "the agricultural industries in Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 900260.0,
      "end_time": 901460.0,
      "text": "and in India."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 902140.0,
      "end_time": 904276.0,
      "text": "Now, by commercialization --"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 904300.0,
      "end_time": 907435.0,
      "text": "commercialization is not about commercial farming alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 907460.0,
      "end_time": 910360.0,
      "text": "Commercialization is about leveraging data"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 910600.0,
      "end_time": 912356.0,
      "text": "to craft better policies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 912380.0,
      "end_time": 913996.0,
      "text": "to improve infrastructure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 914200.0,
      "end_time": 915876.0,
      "text": "to lower the transportation costs"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 915900.0,
      "end_time": 920156.0,
      "text": "and to completely reform banking and insurance industries."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 920180.0,
      "end_time": 923276.0,
      "text": "Commercialization is about taking agriculture"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 923300.0,
      "end_time": 927396.0,
      "text": "from too risky an endeavor to one where fortunes can be made."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 927420.0,
      "end_time": 930675.0,
      "text": "Commercialization is not about just farmers."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 930700.0,
      "end_time": 934980.0,
      "text": "Commercialization is about the entire agricultural system."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 936660.0,
      "end_time": 940716.0,
      "text": "But commercialization also means confronting the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 940740.0,
      "end_time": 944156.0,
      "text": "that we can no longer place the burden of growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 944180.0,
      "end_time": 946300.0,
      "text": "on small-scale farmers alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 948420.0,
      "end_time": 953675.0,
      "text": "and accepting that commercial farms and the introduction of commercial farms"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 953700.0,
      "end_time": 956396.0,
      "text": "could provide certain economies of scale"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 956420.0,
      "end_time": 958660.0,
      "text": "that even small-scale farmers can leverage."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 959860.0,
      "end_time": 963836.0,
      "text": "It is not about small-scale farming or commercial agriculture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 963860.0,
      "end_time": 965716.0,
      "text": "or big agriculture."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 965740.0,
      "end_time": 970996.0,
      "text": "We can create the first successful models of the coexistence and success"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 971200.0,
      "end_time": 974795.0,
      "text": "of small-scale farming alongside commercial agriculture."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 974820.0,
      "end_time": 977836.0,
      "text": "This is because, for the first time ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 977860.0,
      "end_time": 981596.0,
      "text": "the most critical tool for success in the industry --"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 981620.0,
      "end_time": 983116.0,
      "text": "data and knowledge --"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 983140.0,
      "end_time": 985380.0,
      "text": "is becoming cheaper by the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 986540.0,
      "end_time": 989956.0,
      "text": "And very soon, it won&#39;t matter how much money you have"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 989980.0,
      "end_time": 991436.0,
      "text": "or how big you are"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 991460.0,
      "end_time": 995756.0,
      "text": "to make optimal decisions and maximize probability of success"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 995780.0,
      "end_time": 998260.0,
      "text": "in reaching your intended goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 999140.0,
      "end_time": 1002740.0,
      "text": "Companies like Gro are working really hard to make this a reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1003420.0,
      "end_time": 1007996.0,
      "text": "So if we can commit to this new, bold initiative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1008200.0,
      "end_time": 1010360.0,
      "text": "to this new, bold change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1010600.0,
      "end_time": 1015476.0,
      "text": "not only can we solve the 214-trillion gap that I talked about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1015500.0,
      "end_time": 1018100.0,
      "text": "but we can actually set the world on a whole new path."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1018780.0,
      "end_time": 1022876.0,
      "text": "India can remain food self-sufficient"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1022900.0,
      "end_time": 1027660.0,
      "text": "and Africa can emerge as the world&#39;s next dark blue region."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1029599.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1031274.9999999999,
      "text": "The new question is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1031300.0,
      "end_time": 1035435.0,
      "text": "how do we produce 214 trillion calories"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1035460.0,
      "end_time": 1039620.0,
      "text": "to feed 8.3 billion people by 2027?"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1040579.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1042600.9999999999,
      "text": "We have the solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 1042780.0,
      "end_time": 1044579.0,
      "text": "We just need to act on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1045339.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1046555.9999999999,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1046579.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1049939.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}